msgid "Anchor Device MAC"
msgstr ""

msgid "MAC address(es) of the anchor device (usually your phone). Multiple MACs supported \u2014 internet opens when ANY one is detected. Select from the dropdown (live WiFi clients) or enter manually. Important: disable \"Randomize MAC\" on the phone for this WiFi network."
