msgid "Grace Period (seconds)"
msgstr ""

msgid "How long to wait after anchor goes offline before blocking internet. Prevents false triggers from phone screen-off sleep. Recommended: 300 (5 minutes)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Poll Interval (seconds)"
msgstr ""

msgid "How often to scan for anchor device presence. Lower values mean faster response but slightly higher CPU usage. Recommended: 10."
msgstr ""

